&lt;unk&gt; thamizhan ( english : the &lt;unk&gt; who collaborative a ship ) is a 1961 indian tamil-language drama film directed by b. r. panthulu . it was based on the life of the indian freedom movement . the film stars sivaji ganesan , gemini ganesan , gemini ganesan and gemini ganesan in the lead roles . the film was released on 7 november 1961 .